name: PATIENT_SOURCE_COUNT_XML
value: select SUBSTRING(sourcesystem_cd,POSITION('_' in sourcesystem_cd)+1) as patient_range, count(distinct patient_num) as patient_count from i2b2demodata.observation_fact where sourcesystem_cd <> 'post_processing' and patient_num in (select distinct patient_num from DX) group by patient_range

name: PATIENT_SITE_COUNT_XML
value: select CASE  	WHEN SUBSTRING(sourcesystem_cd,POSITION('_' in sourcesystem_cd)+1) IN ('ARCN ALLIANCE ERA','ARCN ALLIANCE KIRA','lungenclinic_grosshansdorf','ARCN GeKo DFG','ARCN GeKo FZB','ARCN HDM','ARCN NEIC','lungenclinic_grosshansdorf','lungenclinic_grosshansdorf') THEN 'ARCN'  	WHEN SUBSTRING(sourcesystem_cd,POSITION('_' in sourcesystem_cd)+1) IN ('Hannover ARDS','Asthma Hannover','Bronchiektasen Hannover','CF Hannover','COPD Hannover','DPLD Hannover','ELD Hannover','LC Hannover','PH Hannover') THEN 'BREATH'  	WHEN SUBSTRING(sourcesystem_cd,POSITION('_' in sourcesystem_cd)+1) IN ('HUB Hannover CAPNETZ v1','Capnetz v2','HUB Hannover pedCAPNETZ') THEN 'CAPNETZ'  	WHEN SUBSTRING(sourcesystem_cd,POSITION('_' in sourcesystem_cd)+1) IN ('CPCM') THEN 'CPCM'  	WHEN SUBSTRING(sourcesystem_cd,POSITION('_' in sourcesystem_cd)+1) IN ('TLRC Thorax','TLRC CF','TLRC DKFZ','TLRC PLI Cosyconet TP1','TLRC PLI Cosyconet TP2') THEN 'TLRC'  	WHEN SUBSTRING(sourcesystem_cd,POSITION('_' in sourcesystem_cd)+1) IN ('celsius 37','copd_giessen','humane_lungen_giessen','ipf_giessen','kerkhoff_register','nupre_giessen','ph_register_giessen','starlims_giessen') THEN 'UGMLC'  	WHEN SUBSTRING(sourcesystem_cd,POSITION('_' in sourcesystem_cd)+1) IN ('cosyconet') THEN 'COSYCONET'  	ELSE 'UNDEFINED' || SUBSTRING(sourcesystem_cd,POSITION('_' in sourcesystem_cd)+1) END as patient_range, count(distinct patient_num) as patient_count from i2b2demodata.observation_fact where sourcesystem_cd <> 'post_processing' and patient_num in (select distinct patient_num from DX) group by patient_range
